      "text": "要向好看不向坏看",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 67.36,
      "time_str": "01:07.360",
      "text": "这世界有太多不如意",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 72.34,
      "time_str": "01:12.340",
      "text": "但你的生活还是要继续",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 77.73,
      "time_str": "01:17.730",
      "text": "太阳每天依旧要升起",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 83.07,
      "time_str": "01:23.070",
      "text": "希望永远种在你心里",
